│ 2.  The corrected signed remainder simplification logic within a helper function used by `simplifyDivRem`. The new logic uses `computeConstantRange` to get the range of the dividend    │
│ and `ConstantRange::contains` to accurately check if the dividend's absolute value is less than the divisor's absolute value.                                                            │
